<!-- Setup -->
<h3>Setup</h3>

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>2p: cover city of Maracaibo with Maracaibo city tile</li>
                <li>3p or 4p: Maracaibo city tile is not used</li>
                <li>Include city tiles with matching player count</li>
                <li>Use both tiles with "helm" icon, and randomly choose 2 more</li>
                <li>randomly place the 4 tiles on Puerto Plata, Santo Domingo, Port Royal, and Cartagena</li>
                <li>Separate project cards
                    <ul>
                        <li>A-cards (dark rope) 56</li>
                        <li>B-cards (light rope) 101</li>
                        <li>deal 8 A-cards to each player</li>
                        <li>count 40 B-cards and shuffle into remaining A-cards</li>
                        <li>reveal top 4 cards of deck</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>shuffle and add 4 prestige buildings
                    <ul>
                        <li>1 face up</li>
                        <li>3 face down</li>
                        <li>variant: all face up</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>2p: add ownership markers
                    <ul>
                        <li>red -> #6 (San Juan)</li>
                        <li>white -> #7 (St. Kitts)</li>
                        <li>blue -> #8 (Martinique)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Player Setup</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>2 figures</li>
                <li>2 career cards, choose 1 and add 1 figure to each of its 3 spaces</li>
                <li>$8 / 9 / 10 / 11</li>
                <li>Keep 4 cards, add 1 card to planning area, discard 3 cards</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Uprising</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>add B-cards</li>
                <li>add new career cards</li>
                <li>add two new city tiles</li>
                <li>replace quest tiles so they match new ship boards</li>
                <li>add scenario cards 74, 78, 79, 193 to base game</li>
            </ul>


        </div>
    </div>
</div>

